"},{"pid":"40c2a1891027dc6683a85a403116e35e144f34b5","tid":1322073,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c396073b9c5eb546d7f828ae50a92dbe273609e","tid":1322073,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"198cffb53f43b8af68660fe908e2c2b8d3b10a8d","tid":1322073,"uid":51747,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:23:56.000Z","msg":"作者名掉轉咗寫呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:34:44.000Z","msg":"唔驚大陸中原地產收皮咩<br />\n咁話共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要upload上微博先得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:37:56.000Z","msg":"大陸中原都開始收緊皮"},{"pid":"922fb4e11447eba32629eb3dce871f3afa7f4b1a","tid":1322073,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e3276261a5b7b2a025aa4b038bc751813b47b0d","tid":1322073,"uid":38991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:30:11.000Z","msg":"睇埋佢今日個篇先講<br />\n根本係奶共屎忽鬼<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.am\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=fc788cfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am</a>730.c <a href=\"http://om.hk/column/share/180627[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fom.hk%2Fcolumn%2Fshare%2F180627%5B%2Furl%5D&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=ebda8fca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">om.hk/column/share/180627[/url]</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:41:11.000Z","msg":"又轉移個重點<br />\n<br />\n就係反對派成功左，都會因為反對派冇從政經驗/我覺得你地唔得黎話所以你地成功之後都會搞死香港，所以我唔支持<br />\n<br />\n我本身都有深藍既親戚提出過呢個觀點，你地成功左咁又點？政治既野你地識咩？<br />\n<br />\n我想講到時自有選舉，選舉前個個人都會出政綱，咁投票前都比對哂先投架啦大佬，再講民選出黎既特首、議員，點都好過1200票「選」出黎既特首同功能組別啦屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民選最重要既一點係，被選出黎果個始終要做d野黎維持番選民既支持，甚至爭取更多人既支持，所以點解話其實香港依家個情況換做其他國家既民選政府一早倒左台，而港共政府點解冇倒台？因為佢地唔需要人民既支持，只係需要共匪無限量既大力支持就夠，佢地諗住咁就可以隻手遮天"},{"pid":"ebf179bf8dae9b95edc4f702ce47fad497b4acb9","tid":1322073,"uid":98860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:46:29.000Z","msg":"一個城市要改變都咁困難, 一個國家要改變談何容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f4f5ad904849f1aad298dec48772147127e9dfd","tid":1322073,"uid":216664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:46:36.000Z","msg":"施永青都反了，睇黎上面開始唔掂"},{"pid":"7964da040a0f47308373d418f000faacd93b520b","tid":1322073,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:47:20.000Z","msg":"正常返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aceb37d25a513e1303af6aca52cd3e86b6168b42","tid":1322073,"uid":273889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:47:25.000Z","msg":"奶共屍竟然會講人話？<br />\n<br />\nbtw奶共屍係 施永青 喎，係咪同一個人"},{"pid":"66cb08a9348b5e27df46df44fcf321499377c809","tid":1322073,"uid":268619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900ab1548442574b91ce077ca173cf990f83e56d","tid":1322073,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:50:19.000Z","msg":"［建制議員應總辭］39嘆冷氣逗人工議員拎光環譴責暴力，何君堯關鍵缺席聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320529</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f792209ab5dbf73700bfa55960d634d7ce5a0619","tid":1322073,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e3276261a5b7b2a025aa4b038bc751813b47b0d","tid":1322073,"uid":38991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:30:11.000Z","msg":"睇埋佢今日個篇先講<br />\n根本係奶共屎忽鬼<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.am\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%